{
  "title": "ISic002868. I.Sicily inscription 002868",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κορνηλί\n                    ου Κτη\n                    στου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κορνηλί\n                    ου\">Κορνηλί-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ου̣</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κτη\n                    στου\">Κτη-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>στ̣ου</span></span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἕρμος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἕρμος\">Ἕ[ρ]μος</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κορνηλί\n                    ου Κτη\n                    στου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κορνηλί\n                    ου\">ΚΟΡΝΗΛΙ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>Ο.</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κτη\n                    στου\">ΚΤΗ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>Σ.ΟΥ</span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἕρμος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἕρμος\">Ε[.]ΜΟΣ</span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of I.Lipara</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p> Line 3 is problematic: I.Lipara treats 'Hermos' as a distinct name (in the index), presumably because in the nominative, and not easily compatible with the nomen and cognomen of lines 1-2 in the genitive (and so the individual erecting the tombstone?). But bearing in mind that the rho is hypothetical, alternative solutions should be considered.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 45.1381.99 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Bernabò Brea and Cavalier 1994 no.99 pl.133 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002156\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002156</a></li><li>   Bernabó-Brea  Cavalier  Campagna  2003 703 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
